Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DRAGON MASTERS APPROACH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:02:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been years\Nsince we three have gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To require all of us must mean\Nsomething big is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the time come to burn the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, Dino, is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Dino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero Dai, who fights\Nthe Dark Army is my son, Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cruel twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already fought the party he leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their bond of unity was stronger than I\Nanticipated, and I sustained some wounds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were wounded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you came to Argo Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where the Fountain of Miracles\Nthat heals Dragon Knights is located.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't my only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He means his wife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand, Master Baran.\NYou need our help to reclaim Master Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. My son has\Nsome troublesome allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They would risk death for Dai, the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the two Legion Commanders\Nwho betrayed the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast King Crocodine and Dark Swordsman\NHyunckel are not to be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No Legion Commander of the Dark Army\Naside from you could stand up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be the most powerful Dragon Riders\Nof all Darklings and Beastlings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but humans can display terrifying strength\Nwhen they're prepared to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If his allies should resist,\Nyou three must crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, I shall reclaim my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I must prepare for battle.\NWait for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Baran is ever the cautious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just a few humans\Nand a couple of traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your tongue, Galdandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. They say a lion\Ndoes not hold back when killing a hare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget his caution has made\Nour glorious Dragon Legion undefeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it already.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soara, this time I shall get Dino back...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from those filthy humans!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Legion shall now\Nhead to Teran Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When my son, Dino, joins us,\Nour strength shall be absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With everyone calling you "Princess,"\NI wondered who you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the ruler of Papnica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, small as Teran may be,\Nits king would not so easily hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty will see you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not feeling well and asks that\Nyou forgive an audience in his chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait outside.\NCall me when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So that supernatural storm\Nwas caused by the Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And this child is the Dragon Knight's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been a Psychic Signal\Nthat took his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A Psychic Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as a mental wave\Nemitted from the Dragon Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we restore his memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We merely worship the God of Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We know of the Dragon Knight,\Nbut not of the full breadth of its powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then will you let us use this castle\Nto shelter Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You still seek to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Teran may think of\NBaran's attack as divine will,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's an aggression against humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fight against aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I had heard of the bravery\Nof the Princess of Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You will aid Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, are you the famed Seer...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am Nabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my granddaughter, Meruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You possess power\Nbeyond that of your grandmother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Recently, she's been able to\Nsense things I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power shall soon show you\Nterrifying and horrible things to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not resent your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It shall eventually help save humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust that that day shall come\Nand live strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming! An energy of such wrath!\NStraight for this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Other similar energies... Three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out! Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't a prison cell going too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the deepest,\Nmost impregnable place in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady, do you know\Nwhat "imprinting" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when an animal hatches from its egg,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and assumes\Nthe first thing it sees is its parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran's reduced Dai to a state\Nof a newly hatched infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dai encounters Baran now,\Nhe'll probably accept Baran as his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They bear the same mark\Nas irrefutable proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cruel, but this is\Nthe only way to prevent that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of the rest.\NPlease guard the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I could not do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're headed straight for Teran\Nfrom the southeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you show them, Old Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the three sources of energy\Naside from Baran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they be the Dragon Masters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Masters?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The most powerful Dragon Riders\Nthat serve Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With Dragons under their control, they're said\Nto rival even the Legion Commanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean he's brought three guys\Neach as strong as you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may not be strong enough\Nto hold them back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting Baran alone was difficult enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only Hyunckel was here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for. I guess that blows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not about to\Ndie for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bailing now.\NYou guys do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying I'm getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're that strong, there's no point\Nin resisting. What a crock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, do you understand\Nwhat you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's like this and we're falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're facing the most powerful Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to be crazy\Nto consider fighting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought fighting for your friends,\Neven when there's no hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was what you\NDisciples of Aban believed in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dai falls into their hands now,\Nthe human world will end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NI thought you were Dai's best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really willing\Nto abandon Dai now and run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him.\NHe's not even human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of them.\NWhy not give him back to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll take good care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't enlist the aid of one like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's a relief. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not follow him, Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you here to defend this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always admired the Disciples of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If Master Aban was still alive,\NI was hoping to learn from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed Popp would stay with us\Nbecause he's a Disciple of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your courage, Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...? Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When you said Dai was your friend\Neven if he was a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Were those words...\NThose tears... All of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when Maam punched me\Nand said I disgusted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this isn't like back then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I tried to go alone, you'd stop me.\NThat's why I had to say that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look after Dai, everyone!\NI'll stop them, even if I die trying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may not win, but I'll take\None or two of them out with me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So take care of the rest!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&} \NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.59,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABREAK{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going any farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's here to stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the others lying in wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't seem like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?! Or just an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Victory to the quick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Galdandy, don't underestimate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He wields spells\Nstronger than you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That scrawny wimp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Betan!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for lifting me up!\NYou're a real help, Ruud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! One escaped above!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Such weak Dragons! Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're brave to try to stop us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Baran, leave this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall catch up,\Nso you should hurry to Master Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't underestimate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it before,\Nhumans who are prepared to die
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,can display terrifying strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"A cornered rat will bite a cat."\NYou never know what the desperate will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what the humans say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Know your place, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A pipsqueak like you couldn't fight\NMaster Baran in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With a single breath...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all you've got, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you could fight\Nthe Dragon Masters with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to make me laugh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Too frail, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Borahorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing more than a fledgling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make him suffer.\NJust drop him on this and end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.\NFor a toy, he's not very fun to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Galdandy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this toy\Nif you two don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a juicy human prey! It's no fun\Nunless we take our time killing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As cruel as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're strong! They're going to kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! If I'm going to die,\NI have to hit them at least once or twice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise, what's the point in me dying?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. Are you dead already, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It hurts! I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Just end it by biting off my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. Since you asked so nicely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you can do anything\Nif you're desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it. That kid killed\NGaldandy's favorite Ethereal Serpent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The rat actually bit the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But his resistance comes at a steep price.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That takes care of their Dragons.\NThe real fight starts now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel! This is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you crying about, birdface?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've killed tons of humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed tons of humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This Ethereal Serpent, Ruud,\Nwas the only friend I ever trusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He was like my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We were always together, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you compare my beloved Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to some filthy little humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these feathers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slice you to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So much that\Nthey'll never find your pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! They're all on the ground now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Betan!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My spell's not working?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use\Nsuch powerful spells anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Magic Power is leaking out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Those white feathers\Ndrain an enemy's Magic Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And these red feathers, drain stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to reduce you to\Nan empty rag doll before I slice you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you fear for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merami!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good! I feel weak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dragging this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this and this and this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?! I bet it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone mad. Even we can't stop him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy could've died painlessly\Nif he hadn't resisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're braver than I thought.\NThat pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to fight back! While I still have\Nstamina and Magic Power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I like that face right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'll do what you did to Ruud!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow your head off like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's the look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep that face!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. I'm saved by\Nthe last guy I want saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
